          śǝllāse-type)</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ኤዎስጣቴዎስ፡ እንዘ፡ እልፍ፡ ውሉድ፡ ውስተ፡ ሕፅንከ፡ </dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ʾEwosṭātewos ʾǝnza ʾǝlf wǝlud wǝsta ḥǝḍnǝka (Qǝne of the śǝllāse-type)</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">ʾEwosṭātewos, when 10 000 children were in your guardianship…</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Qǝne poem on ʾEwosṭātewos</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene/title/t2" xml:lang="en"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ ወርኃ፡ ተድላ፡ ኮኖሙ፡ ለአዕባነ፡ ፍኖት፡ አፈ፡</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene/title/t3" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ʾƎsma warḫā tadlā konomu la-ʾaʿbāna fǝnot ʾafa</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">When its month is delight, there was a brim of the stones of the way…</dc:title><dc:source rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient9798"/><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT7038Qene/part/div1"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene"><ecrm:P129_is_about rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3934Ewostate"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene"><saws:formsPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7037Qene"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3934Ewostate"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2025-07-01+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>ʾEwosṭātewos</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene/person/annotation/2"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7038Qene"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3934Ewostate"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org